Global context: Cody understands your entire codebase, even the code that isn’t on your local machine. Works with code hosted on Bitbucket, GitHub, GitLab, Perforce, and more.

Deployment flexibility: Use Cody Enterprise in a managed single-tenant cloud deployment or host it yourself.

LLM choice: Choose from Claude 2, GPT-4, StarCoder, and more. Alternatively, bring your own LLM key for an even more secure and private environment.

